d":2368884,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T15:46:57.000Z","msg":"Sorry, 我指響德國支持度"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T15:48:39.000Z","msg":"今次排第二，好大機會入到執政聯盟做內閣，所以外長由佢揾人嚟做係可以期待下嘅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T15:50:36.000Z","msg":"冇望上第一位？差好遠架？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T15:51:04.000Z","msg":"睇#21"},{"pid":"70ae2ddfa08b002f4057725c023c590565e8f3dc","tid":2368884,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T15:52:45.000Z","msg":"唉，德國其實就等於成個歐盟立場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39cef17c02097ce944f004f11ce646243c4f125a","tid":2368884,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"70ae2ddfa08b002f4057725c023c590565e8f3dc","tid":2368884,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T15:52:45.000Z","msg":"唉，德國其實就等於成個歐盟立場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T15:55:09.000Z","msg":"唔可以噉睇，當然德國對歐盟未來走向好重要，但歐盟實際上會點行有好多方面要睇<br />\n<br />\n只係我會講，你唔使望佢會好似肥奧噉反支，唔關佢係咪奶共事，而係佢係唔可能做到噉樣"},{"pid":"3d72965a23375bd2b44d54488e6d18f3dec930a1","tid":2368884,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39cef17c02097ce944f004f11ce646243c4f125a","tid":2368884,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"70ae2ddfa08b002f4057725c023c590565e8f3dc","tid":2368884,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T15:52:45.000Z","msg":"唉，德國其實就等於成個歐盟立場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T15:55:09.000Z","msg":"唔可以噉睇，當然德國對歐盟未來走向好重要，但歐盟實際上會點行有好多方面要睇<br />\n<br />\n只係我會講，你唔使望佢會好似肥奧噉反支，唔關佢係咪奶共事，而係佢係唔可能做到噉樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T15:59:50.000Z","msg":"咁你覺得支歐協議簽唔簽得成？"}]}